它看起来很好吃。

118
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:27,340
Okay, very good.
好的，非常好。

119
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:31,620
And Andrea was worried because Manny is ordering so much food.
Andrea 很担心，因为 Manny 点了太多食物。

